%% AlmaAssist — User Flow Diagram

graph TD
    A[Landing Page] --> B{Authenticated?}
    B -->|No| C[Sign Up Page]
    B -->|No| D[Login Page]
    C --> E[Create Account]
    E --> F[Dashboard]
    D --> F

    F --> G[New Questionnaire]
    F --> H[View Past Questionnaires]

    G --> I[Upload Questionnaire PDF]
    I --> J[Upload Reference Documents 1-8]
    J --> K[Process Documents]
    K --> L[pdf-parse extracts text]
    L --> M[Gemini extracts questions]
    M --> N[Store in Firestore]
    N --> O[Review Page]

    H --> O

    O --> P[Click Generate Answers]
    P --> Q[For Each Question]
    Q --> R[Fetch all reference doc text]
    R --> S[Send question + docs to Gemini]
    S --> T[Gemini returns answer + citation + confidence + evidence]
    T --> U[Update Firestore]
    U --> Q

    O --> V[Review Answers]
    V --> W{Edit needed?}
    W -->|Yes| X[Edit Answer Inline]
    X --> Y[Save to Firestore]
    Y --> V
    W -->|No| Z[Export PDF]
    Z --> AA[jsPDF generates PDF]
    AA --> AB[Download Completed Questionnaire]

    O --> AC[Coverage Summary]
    AC --> AD[Total / Answered / Not Found]
